txt.en: Destroy heraldry of Sauron in Arandor ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Heraldry of Sauron can be found in Arandor.\n\nYou should destroy any heraldry of Sauron that you find in Arandor.

'Have you seen the banners of the Dark Lord that still stand upon the Kingsland? Even one would be too many! Sauron thinks to intimidate our soldiers? Bah! Seek out the banners and remove them at once!'
Heraldry of Sauron still waves above the Kingsland of Arandor.
